      local Lib = loadstring(game:HttpGet("رابط_المحرك"))()

    [ 2. المزايا المتوفرة ]:
    - 50 ثيم (Theme): اختر أي لون مثل "Cyber", "Toxic", "Magma", "Blood".
    - الشعار العائم: يظهر أيقونة قابلة للسحب لفتح/إغلاق القائمة.
    - حماية الإغلاق: تظهر رسالة تأكيد عند محاولة إغلاق السكربت.
    - الترتيب الجانبي (Tab Sections): يمكنك تقسيم التابات لعناوين (Main, Combat, Misc).

    [ 3. طريقة الإضافة (الترتيب البرمجي) ]:
    - أولاً: إنشاء النافذة -> local Win = Lib:CreateWindow({Name = "اسمك", Theme = "ثيم"})
    - ثانياً: تقسيم الجانب (اختياري) -> Win:AddTabSection("العنوان")
    - ثالثاً: إنشاء التاب -> local MyTab = Win:CreateTab("اسم التاب")
    - رابعاً: إضافة العناصر (Button, Toggle, Slider, Dropdown, Input, Keybind, Paragraph, Section).

    ================================================================================
    [ ENGLISH - Developer's Reference ]
    ================================================================================
    
    [ 1. Getting Started ]:
    - Upload this framework and get the Raw Link.
    - Fetch the library in your main script using: 
      local Lib = loadstring(game:HttpGet("YOUR_LINK"))()

    [ 2. Key Features ]:
    - 50 Built-in Themes: Switch colors easily by name (e.g., "Electric", "Midnight").
    - Floating Icon: A draggable button that toggles UI visibility.
    - Safe Exit: Confirmation dialog (Yes/No) to prevent accidental closing.
    - Sidebar Organization: Use 'TabSections' to categorize your menus.

    [ 3. Script Structure (Hierarchy) ]:
    - Window First: local Win = Lib:CreateWindow({Name = "Title", Theme = "Theme"})
    - Tab Section: Win:AddTabSection("Header Name")
    - Create Tab: local Tab = Win:CreateTab("Tab Name")
    - Add Elements: Inside the tab, add (Buttons, Toggles, Sliders, Dropdowns, etc).

    ================================================================================
    [ EXAMPLE CODE / مثال عملي سريع ]
    ================================================================================
    
